{"tid":1280932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ CHAN 見到請你入黎！！","createTime":"2019-07-03T06:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:33:25.000Z","uid":190550,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69c0f36cd6c46b84b9e2c537214fc6c20c9f802e","tid":1280932,"uid":190550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:33:09.000Z","msg":"你安全冇事就最好<br />\n你知唔知我地幾緊張你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班手足冒住俾狗點相既風險走出黎搵你<br />\n隔離post有個女仔有性侵陰影都克服咗<br />\n就係為左保護你呀<br />\n<br />\n朋友話頭先有幾個姨姨係PP為咗搵你<br />\n俾經過既藍屍鬧 叫佢地去死<br />\n幾個姨姨聽到嬲到喊出黎<br />\n佢地好心到準備飯盒俾大家<br />\n陪大家舉牌 就係唔想再失去多一個手足<br />\n我聽見都心痛<br />\n<br />\n你真係要好好珍惜自己<br />\n你杳無音信既時候大家心情都好負面<br />\n我都好怕會有更多人做傻事<br />\n<br />\n我地一定長命過林鄭架嘛<br />\n所以唔好再咁傻豬亂諗<br />\n我地一個都不能少㗎知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55a3221fff3f086e4ca09a655ed1ee20618e231","tid":1280932,"uid":190550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"唔記得講埋<br />\n好多謝今日有份出黎既手足<br />\n令我覺得香港仲有希望！"},{"pid":"56fb4d79155fc840093fb48ff551c78c50bce8a3","tid":1280932,"uid":272964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bea8ce4ede9732e582f86d91c1697847106ed27","tid":1280932,"uid":66748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"peace"},{"pid":"d2ea25b07f486d5abd6a69ba11d8c3fa3c075578","tid":1280932,"uid":98611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"共同進退"}]}